.head 3 +  General Window Class: clsGeneralSender
.head 4 -  Description: Commincates between clsGeneralSender and clsGeneralReceiver
Step 1: Set hWndReceiver and or nCommIDKey ( optional number that identifies this communication )
Step 2: Call SendNumber( .. ), SendString( .. ), SendDateTime( .. ) or SendWndHandle( .. )
repeatedly to perform comminication
