.head 3 +  General Window Class: clsGeneralReceiver
.head 4 -  Description: Commincates between clsGeneralSender and clsGeneralReceiver
Step 1: Trap message PAM_clsCOM_SENDNOTIFY ( wParam = nCommIDKey ) and call
GetNumberX( ), GetStringX( ), GetDateTimeX( ) or GetWndHandleX( )
to RECEIVE values IN the SAME ORDER as they were sent.
